<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.4.2">
<l>kāṉiṭai yuruvaic cuṭucaran turantu kaṇṭumuṅ</l>
<l>koṭuntoḻi luravōṉ</l>
<l>ūṉuṭai yakalat taṭukaṇai kuḷippa vuyirkkavarn</l>
<l>tukantavem moruvaṉ</l>
<l>tēṉuṭaik kamalat tayaṉoṭu tēvar ceṉṟuceṉ</l>
<l>ṟiṟaiñciṭa peruku</l>
<l>vāṉiṭai mutunīrk kaṅkaiyiṉ karaimēl</l>
<l>vatariyāc ciramat tuḷḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Rejoiced, robbing a life, when he pierced a murderous bolt</l>
<l rend="indent">into the fleshy chest of the strong one of cruel deeds,</l>
<l>He is the one in Badarī Āśrama on the banks of the Ganges,</l>
<l rend="indent">[its] ancient waters swelling from heaven,</l>
<l>While celestials, arriving continually, worship</l>
<l rend="indent">along with the Unborn [Brahmā] of the honeyed lotus.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
